@startuml seq-16-notification-manual-send
title POST /notifications/send — manual announcement (Admin / Manager)

actor "AdminOrManager" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/notifications" as API <<service>>
participant "requireRole\n(ADMIN|MANAGER)" as R <<service>>
participant "saveUploadedFile" as FS <<service>>
participant "createNotification" as CN <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

B -> API: multipart: title, body?,\ntargetType, optional dept/role,\noptional attachment

API -> R: role + manager rules\n(department-only for managers)
alt Forbidden target
  API --> B: 403
else OK
  opt attachment file
    API -> FS: allocateStorageKey + save buffer
  end
  API -> CN: createNotification(MANUAL, actor, target, meta…)
  CN -> DB: resolve + insert rows
  alt notifId null (no recipients)
    API -> FS: deleteFileIfExists(attachment)\n(best effort)
    API --> B: 200 { notificationId: null, message }
  else Created
    API --> B: 201 { notificationId }
  end
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/notifications.ts** (~181+),
  **notificationService.createNotification**.
end note

@enduml
